longName: init innovation in traffic systems SE
longBusinessSummary: init innovation in traffic systems SE provides intelligent transportation systems solutions for public transportation worldwide. The company develops, produces, integrates, installs, and maintains software and hardware products for transport companies. It offers research and development, planning and dispatching, analyzing and optimizing, ticketing and fare management, operations control and real-time passenger information, and service and maintenance solutions. The company was founded in 1983 and is based in Karlsruhe, Germany.
